		"description": "<p>Fire genasi, also called volcani (singular: volcanus), are born in places where elemental fire makes its magic known. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<p><strong>Fire Magic. </strong>You know the produce flame cantrip. You can cast burning hands once per long rest. Your spellcasting ability for these spells is your choice of Constitution, Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma.</p>\n<p><strong>Darkvision.&nbsp;</strong>Your internal fires grant you superior vision in dark and dim conditions. You can see in dim light within 60 feet of you as if it were bright light, and in darkness as if it were dim light. You can&rsquo;t discern color in darkness, all things are tinged shades of red.</p>",
